great release, but we've done

00:15:02.106 --> 00:15:02.886 A:middle
more.

00:15:03.016 --> 00:15:03.836 A:middle
Much more.

00:15:04.106 --> 00:15:05.296 A:middle
And we have a lot to cover

00:15:05.296 --> 00:15:08.196 A:middle
